{
  "stem": "17337.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 246.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it could be another 5 kilometer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't so far.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It took maybe a couple hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On-- when we got-- the first thing when we got into Plaszow, naturally, we had to-- to-- to leave it on the floor, everything we had with us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they allow you still to take some-- some personal things, they still allow you to take.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But most importantly, [INAUDIBLE] you have money or jewelry, you know, and if you say no, and they looked, and they-- they shot you on the spot, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But right-- the same-- the first day when we came into Plaszow, so they didn't took us to barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us what they call it an appeals place, in other words, like the a-- a assembly place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were already thousands of people assembled there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we coming there, they were hanging three people, three young boys where they were hung that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, we found out the reason they were hung up because they were whistling a Russian song.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is a very popular song, 'Volga Volga,' [SPEAKING NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means Volga is the Russian, you know, river.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's why they-- they hung them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, you see, the-- the guards in Plaszow were Ukrainian, but they were many time worse than Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they understand Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's-- that was the first day, our reception in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And down they sent us in barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the following day, they-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they make groups, you know, for-- for 10 or 15 people and were sending us to work, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we-- we arrived in-- in Plaszow, that must have be [INAUDIBLE] end '42 of beginning '43.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- could be beginning of '43.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wintertime?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
